subject: Track and Field
Olympic Games
lead_paragraph: Cam Levins was the star of the Armory Track Invitational in Manhattan, pulling off a stunning double win in the one-mile and two-mile races and beating the Olympic silver medalist Galen Rupp in completing the feat.
